ass=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span class=\"token operator\">++</span>j<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span>\n           <span class=\"token function\">printf</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"%d \"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>rotate<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>i<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>j<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n       <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#125;</span>\n       <span class=\"token function\">printf</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"\\n\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n   <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#125;</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">&#125;</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"陣列與圖片\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#陣列與圖片\">#</a> 陣列與圖片</h3>\n<p>我們在現實生中也可以使用陣列模擬矩陣達到編輯圖片的效果<br>\n假設現在有一張圖片，四點座標如下</p>\n<p><img data-src=\"https://i.imgur.com/cEPR1BA.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>如果要往左往右移，那就是這些點的 x 座標加減一個數字，上下移就是 y 座標加減數字，放大縮小則是建立向量乘上倍數，旋轉就是乘上旋轉矩陣，鏡像也是透過線性轉換，簡而言之我們只要有辦法建立向量就有辦法用陣列表示再透過線性代數學到的那些矩陣運算得到想要的結果</p>\n<h3 id=\"小節\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#小節\">#</a> 小節</h3>\n<p>本篇文章主要介紹陣列的特性以及陣列作為矩陣的運用，下篇則會介紹一維陣列在多項式加法、進制表示、大數加法的應用，以及陣列題目中非常有名的 magic square 、game of life，祝大家閱讀愉快</p>\n",
